        <p class="text-[#2D2D2D] mb-3"><strong>Description:</strong> Some applications require chemicals to augment the separation process. For example, a demulsifying chemical may help break the emulsion in emulsified oils. A chemical injection port followed by an inline static mixer works well for introducing chemicals.</p>
